songs.title: Don Quan Intro (Squidtastic)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
(*slurp*)
Ahh (*iPhone notification sound*)
We out here on this good sunny day, hold on, hold on
Excuse me Squid
Buy me some shrimps over here with some, with some, with some extra butter, ya know what I'm sayin', haha
But, anyway, it's Don Quan back again-in
Got the mermaids on the beach butt booty naked
Wrapped around our tentacles giving good SANDAS if ya didn't know
King squid over here, know what I'm sayin'?
Coolest squid in the motherfuckin' ocean
Yeah, T3 over there clappin' big cheeks
Know what I'm sayin', we love the thick hoes, huh
We just out here feelin' squidtastic
But this is squidtastic, ya know
And this shit goin' barnacles, nigga
SahBabii, nigga, king squid, nigga, king of the jungle, nigga
Squid that shit up, nigga (Squid that shit up)
